<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首1中0尾异法，方法四，被数（被乘数）加乘个（乘数的个位），后面接着写末位数与末位数的乘积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">速算过程是：被数加乘数的个位->后面接着写个位数与个位数的乘积。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">1005×1009=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 1005×1009</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">被数加乘个(1005+9)×1000</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">后面写末位数与末位数的乘积5×9</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1014045</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>